Name: Elephants Can't Jump
About the game: Elephants Can’t Jump is a side-scrolling puzzle platformer with no jump mechanic (did the title give it away?). Join Akkoro, the salty octopus, and the rambunctious elephant Pengin, as they escape abduction on an alien spaceship. Use Akkoro’s launch ability to fly through the air and puzzle your way from room to room, all the while collecting fellow abductees throughout the ship. Come join the gravity-defying feats of the greatest dodecapedal duo!
